{"tid":341930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女遊客北京遊樂場玩動感影院　從10米高墮地亡","createTime":"2017-07-31T08:03:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T08:26:34.000Z","uid":48093,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"37b7a66b6838941999409d1b738a347584c2b8f2","tid":341930,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:03:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170731/photo/bkncn-20170731154200967-0731_05011_001_01p.jpg?20170731155829\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170731%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170731154200967-0731_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20170731155829&h=ed36f71d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n北京昌平區樂多港奇幻樂園發生嚴重事故。一名51歲丁姓女遊客周日（30日）在園內動感影院「翺翔紫禁」內觀看影片時，從升至約10米高的座椅掉下，墮地身亡。事發後，動感影院門外已放置「設備檢查，暫停開放」的指示牌。目前警方正調查事故原因，初步排除人為傷害。<br />\n<br />\n據園區醫務室醫生透露，當日下午2時許，他接到園區值班經理通知，稱館內有人從上面（座椅上）摔下來，「我到之後看到一位女性遊客躺在地上，邊上很多血，當時已經沒有生命體徵了」。<br />\n<br />\n據該園官網介紹，動感影院「翺翔紫禁」是集大銀幕電影、大型機械控制、實時現場特效等多種高科技於一體項目。遊客經平立式座椅升至10多米高空觀看電影畫面。該項目佔地2430平方米，每場容納100人，體驗時長約6分鐘，日接待量2400人次。"},{"pid":"501c910f50a7bc9cad89da2419ba2cba12f08c2a","tid":341930,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:06:18.000Z","msg":"動感影院唔係最安全既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e43d0a448c37f5c93cbc029f46b43f5b68f7f149","tid":341930,"uid":126293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:06:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f4342fe85b5f8767f833193e17ada59d0d25113","tid":341930,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:07:13.000Z","msg":"中國的會..."},{"pid":"9e8d88ca